{"tid":1965833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港人表示慣咗】英媒爆孫興民軍訓內容 要除豬咀聞TG練射擊","createTime":"2020-04-09T17:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T17:53:16.000Z","uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ecaa6a764651a19ad44a68b4edb407e98bb90334","tid":1965833,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T17:47:11.000Z","msg":"早前本報就曾經報道，南韓球星孫興民趁住英超暫停嘅時間，飛返老家南韓服兵役，接受為期四個禮拜嘅軍事訓練。近日就有英國傳媒揭密，睇下Oppa返到南韓之後要接受咩訓練，當中有一樣係近大半年香港人非常熟悉嘅嘢，就係喺完全沒任何保護之下聞住催淚彈（TG）呼吸。<br />\n<br />\n英國鏡報的報道指出，雖然老孫今次嘅軍訓只係四個禮拜，不過都相當認真。其中佢首先要剃返個類似近期大熱嘅「栗子頭」，之後要參加實彈射擊訓練、又要做30公里嘅負重行軍，之後作戰演習同埋紀律訓練教育呢啲都唔少得。而最慘烈嘅，就係士兵要入一充滿催淚氣體嘅房，然後除低豬咀，喺入面如常呼吸。有指好多士兵訓練完之後都係眼淚、鼻涕，口水齊流，相信香港人對呢個畫面都相當熟悉。<br />\n雖然話四個禮拜嘅軍事訓練，未必好似真係服兵役咁認真，但都有一定嘅危險同難度，而老孫就無耐前先因為手臂骨裂而接受手術，據指熱刺都會同老孫保持聯絡，避色佢因為軍訓舊患復發。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200409/ZJWPHTJIJMJPBMXTAOJIRAWD2Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailysports&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200409%2FZJWPHTJIJMJPBMXTAOJIRAWD2Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailysports%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=29316048\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200409%2FZJWPHTJIJMJPBMXTAOJIRAWD2Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailysports%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6d859151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200409/ZJWPHTJIJMJPBMXTAOJIRAWD2Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailysports&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbf31c546ad9111cbb594fc3f3c0aece7b135b8","tid":1965833,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T17:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46403612b8dd172fe2327fcfc27969900fcf084","tid":1965833,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecaa6a764651a19ad44a68b4edb407e98bb90334","tid":1965833,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T17:47:11.000Z","msg":"早前本報就曾經報道，南韓球星孫興民趁住英超暫停嘅時間，飛返老家南韓服兵役，接受為期四個禮拜嘅軍事訓練。近日就有英國傳媒揭密，睇下Oppa返到南韓之後要接受咩訓練，當中有一樣係近大半年香港人非常熟悉嘅嘢，就係喺完全沒任何保護之下聞住催淚彈（TG）呼吸。<br />\n<br />\n英國鏡報的報道指出，雖然老孫今次嘅軍訓只係四個禮拜，不過都相當認真。其中佢首先要剃返個類似近期大熱嘅「栗子頭」，之後要參加實彈射擊訓練、又要做30公里嘅負重行軍，之後作戰演習同埋紀律訓練教育呢啲都唔少得。而最慘烈嘅，就係士兵要入一充滿催淚氣體嘅房，然後除低豬咀，喺入面如常呼吸。有指好多士兵訓練完之後都係眼淚、鼻涕，口水齊流，相信香港人對呢個畫面都相當熟悉。<br />\n雖然話四個禮拜嘅軍事訓練，未必好似真係服兵役咁認真，但都有一定嘅危險同難度，而老孫就無耐前先因為手臂骨裂而接受手術，據指熱刺都會同老孫保持聯絡，避色佢因為軍訓舊患復發。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200409/ZJWPHTJIJMJPBMXTAOJIRAWD2Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailysports&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200409%2FZJWPHTJIJMJPBMXTAOJIRAWD2Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailysports%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=29316048\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200409%2FZJWPHTJIJMJPBMXTAOJIRAWD2Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailysports%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6d859151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200409/ZJWPHTJIJMJPBMXTAOJIRAWD2Q/?utm_cam